Package: testthis
Type: Package
Title: Utility functions and Rstudio addins to make using the testthat
  package even more fun
Version: 0.0.8.9007
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Fleck", email = "stefan.b.fleck@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Stefan Fleck <stefan.b.fleck@gmail.com>
Description: This package automates menial tasks associated with creating and
  running automated unit tests with the testthat package. It further provides
  Rstudio addins for tasks such as navigating between an R source file and an 
  associated test file, or running tests in a single testfile. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
  assertthat,
  devtools,
  usethis,
  testthat,
  stringi,
  magrittr,
  utils,
  stats,
  rprojroot,
  tools
Suggests:
  knitr,
  rmarkdown,
  rstudioapi
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
